name: Thank you, community - and send me your questions!
description:
Just thrown this together on a Friday evening before catching a train up to Newcastle for the weekend. Thanks again for all your support and I’ll be uploading regularly from now! Make sure you pop your questions in the comment section below!

I have more super channel news which I’ll share with you in a few weeks...stay keen. :-)

See you with 2/25 of #paulsworldtour early next week.
